elements.title: Ravish Malhotra
elements.contents: ... that after training for the Soyuz T-11 mission, Indian Air Force pilot Ravish Malhotra (pictured) stayed on the ground as a backup astronaut for Rakesh Sharma, who became the first Indian in space?

elements.title: Biltmore Theatre
